Record Class BaseDataClient.SendResult

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
grafioschtrader.m2m.client.BaseDataClient.SendResult
Enclosing class:
BaseDataClient
public static record BaseDataClient.SendResult(boolean serverReachable, boolean httpError, int httpStatusCode, MessageEnvelope response, boolean serverBusy) extends Record
Result wrapper for M2M message sending operations. Distinguishes between successful delivery, HTTP errors, and network failures.
